♪When sorrow and joy blend into ink♪

00:00:13.940 --> 00:00:19.340
♪Flowers fade, rain falls,
helpless as time♪

00:00:21.130 --> 00:00:26.460
♪Lament this frail body,
tangled in love and hate♪

