♪I hold out a heart sincere and true♪

00:16:34.410 --> 00:16:36.730
♪Crossing the deep courtyard♪

00:16:37.060 --> 00:16:40.020
♪Just to trade it for one kiss from you♪

00:16:40.020 --> 00:16:42.170
